 product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#L9ECAV7KIM): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"07d12e47-2cc9-4d27-8e4b-92316af85471\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"ca2fbeb9-7095-4f9b-bc7e-4f628926ada4\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:21:33.30175497Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6700f817-2ae3-4232-96e3-ae733039e759\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"a1174572-90a0-4162-bf9d-f1cccce8cb34\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:22:32.2136402Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "service_name": ["productcatalogservice", "frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-06"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-18T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-18T19:29:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-18 19:29:04+00:00"}, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取的链路追踪数据，我将对故障进行分析。从数据中可以看出明显的异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\", \"productcatalogservice->tidb\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"产品目录服务频繁出现'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'错误，这是数据库连接问题导致的\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"从正常耗时约10秒激增至3900万秒（约45天），延迟倍数超过4000倍，表明服务严重不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"错误消息'Region is unavailable'表明底层TiDB数据库区域不可用，这是根因数据库问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **根因定位**：故障根因是TiDB数据库的区域不可用问题（\"Region is unavailable\"），这影响了依赖它的productcatalogservice。\n\n2. **传播路径**：\n   - TiDB数据库不可用 → productcatalogservice异常 → frontend和checkoutservice受影响\n   - 所有调用链的异常都源于对productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作\n\n3. **延迟分析**：\n   - 正常响应时间约10秒，异常期间激增至3900万秒，延迟倍数超过4000倍\n   - 这表明服务完全不可达或处于严重阻塞状态\n\n4. **错误模式**：\n   - 统一的\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"错误\n   - 影响范围包括前端服务、推荐服务、购物车服务等所有依赖产品目录的组件", "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据分析，我发现了一个明显的错误模式。以下是我的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"database error\", \"productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库区域不可用错误 (Error 9005: Region is unavailable)，导致产品查询失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点**：\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：\n   - 所有错误日志都显示相同的错误代码：`Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n   - 错误主要来自 `productcatalogservice` 服务（数据库查询失败）\n   - `frontend` 服务因无法从 `productcatalogservice` 获取产品信息而报错\n\n2. **根本原因分析**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 服务无法连接到数据库或数据库区域不可用\n   - 这导致所有依赖产品目录的服务（如 `frontend`）出现级联故障\n   - 错误从 19:10:46 开始，持续到 19:22:32，影响范围广泛\n\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 直接报告数据库区域不可用错误\n   - `frontend` 服务通过 RPC 调用 `productcatalogservice` 时失败，显示相同的数据库错误\n   - 错误频率高（`productcatalogservice-1` 出现 141 次），表明是持续性故障\n\n根因很可能是 `productcatalogservice` 依赖的数据库服务出现区域可用性问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on the metric analysis, I can identify several key anomalies during the fault period. Let me analyze the findings:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"duration_99th\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"memory_usage\", \"store_unhealth_count\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB数据库性能严重下降，duration_99th从0.01ms飙升到64.88ms(变化率199.94%)，failed_query_ops出现异常，同时memory_usage下降36.37%可能表明内存回收或重启\",\n      \"evidence\": \"duration_99th: 0.01ms → 64.88ms (变化率199.94%), failed_query_ops: 0 → 43.26, memory_usage: 1447550976 → 748777472 (下降36.37%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间rrt严重恶化，从7250.37ms飙升至20164885.29ms(变化率199.86%)，表明该Pod存在严重性能问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt: 7250.37ms → 20164885.29ms (变化率199.86%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio均出现10.34%的错误率，表明该Pod存在服务故障\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0% → 10.34%, client_error_ratio: 0% → 10.34%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个frontend Pod出现高error_ratio和server_error_ratio，frontend-0错误率23.53%，frontend-1错误率28.57%，frontend-2错误率28.57%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: error_ratio 23.53%, frontend-1: error_ratio 28.57%, frontend-2: error_ratio 28.57%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **TiDB数据库严重性能问题** - `tidb-tidb`的99分位响应时间从0.01ms飙升到64.88ms，变化率高达199.94%，同时出现查询失败和内存使用异常\n2. **productcatalogservice-2极端延迟** - 响应时间从7秒飙升至2016万毫秒，表明该Pod完全不可用\n3. **shippingservice-2服务故障** - 出现10.34%的错误率\n4. **前端服务普遍错误** - 所有frontend Pod都出现高错误率(23-28%)\n\n**根因分析优先级：** TiDB数据库性能问题可能是根本原因，导致下游服务(productcatalogservice等)出现连锁故障。"}
