ctcatalogservice-0', 'adservice-2', 'checkoutservice-1', 'currencyservice-2', 'paymentservice-0', 'cartservice-2', 'frontend-2']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的日志数据分析，我发现了一个明显的错误模式。以下是我的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"database error\", \"productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库区域不可用错误 (Error 9005: Region is unavailable)，导致产品查询失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点**：\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：\n   - 所有错误日志都显示相同的错误代码：`Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n   - 错误主要来自 `productcatalogservice` 服务（数据库查询失败）\n   - `frontend` 服务因无法从 `productcatalogservice` 获取产品信息而报错\n\n2. **根本原因分析**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 服务无法连接到数据库或数据库区域不可用\n   - 这导致所有依赖产品目录的服务（如 `frontend`）出现级联故障\n   - 错误从 19:10:46 开始，持续到 19:22:32，影响范围广泛\n\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 直接报告数据库区域不可用错误\n   - `frontend` 服务通过 RPC 调用 `productcatalogservice` 时失败，显示相同的数据库错误\n   - 错误频率高（`productcatalogservice-1` 出现 141 次），表明是持续性故障\n\n根因很可能是 `productcatalogservice` 依赖的数据库服务出现区域可用性问题。\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nBased on the metric analysis, I can identify several key anomalies during the fault period. Let me analyze the findings:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"duration_99th\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"memory_usage\", \"store_unhealth_count\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB数据库性能严重下降，duration_99th从0.01ms飙升到64.88ms(变化率199.94%)，failed_query_ops出现异常，同时memory_usage下降36.37%可能表明内存回收或重启\",\n      \"evidence\": \"duration_99th: 0.01ms → 64.88ms (